hackathon-description-text: 24 hour hackathon at the University of Birmingham, back for the 4th time on 12-13th March. 150 students will come together for a weekend of creativity, collaboration and code.
hackathon-eligibility: Any current university student with a valid ID card from their institution can attend, as well as 14-17 year old school students for the daytimes only.
